  "text": "Oxford-102 [CITATION_1] consists of 102 flower categories, with around 40 and 258 images in each class. The images have large scale, pose, and light variations and some categories are very similar to each other. The model was trained for 30,000 iterations with learning rate reduced after iteration 15,000. The images were saved at resolution of 256 × 256 and randomly cropped to 224 × 224. Then, the cropped images are resized to 64 × 64 for training.",
